<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Checkbox with a red line through it. Next to it is a checkbox with the setting for the main variation.</p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>3 possible conditions:<br>
<strong>Activated</strong> (check mark)<br>
<strong>Deactivated</strong> (no check mark)<br>
