<p>Inherited values are displayed in grey font. Empty fields can also be inherited.</p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Inheritance is automatically deactivated if a text field is cleared, filled with text or if the inherited content is edited.</p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
